ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Iran) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (IRAN) REGULATIONS in order to add five (5) individuals to Schedule 1 of the Regulations, prohibiting them from transacting business with individuals and businesses in Canada unless otherwise authorized by the Minister of the Foreign Affairs.
